{"tid":1286573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"就武漢有可能發生8964翻版，我哋應該整個197x晚會","createTime":"2019-07-05T01:57:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T03:23:09.000Z","uid":23189,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"07d36d5ecbe395819b8023324c91fbe5a7466c9b","tid":1286573,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:57:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">邊個會搞阿？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n陶傑在電台節目中表示，北京最頭痛的問題，並不是平反六四、結束一黨專政這些口號，而是有港人懷著分離意識，不承認自己是中國人，認為六四是「中國人自己的事」。兩害相權之下，中國政府會寧可香港市民參與六四集會。<br />\n<br />\n我認為<br />\n<br />\n1. 武漢可以用嚟換鏡指出「今日武漢 明日香港」嚟提醒自己人同喚醒扮瞓嗰啲，特別係走難落嚟香港嘅上岸離地廢老<br />\n<br />\n2. 鄰國嘅事唔理得咁多，門前雪各自掃，努力爭取五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫手推埋我另一個post，越多人一齊做義士們越安全！<br />\n<br />\n「七黑」團結打倒白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1284973\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1284973</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zm1ytZc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzm1ytZc.jpg&h=68603869&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d06e95775a9a1c6f6d18251597d4acc8aa0302cb","tid":1286573,"uid":200758,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:58:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4833cba1592758f49f3c1b0ae8e9fb2df3dec8f3","tid":1286573,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy